high_descs: Step forward, then turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the rightmost tomato on the white table.
Turn left and go towards the wall, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato inside, chill it, then take it out.
Turn left and go to the sink, then turn left to go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside, and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the white table.
Pick the tomato on the right up from the table.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick up the tomato and shut the door again.
Go left and then left again to face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: place the tomato to cool and then take it out
turn around and head to the oven
place the tomato in the oven
anns.task_desc: place a cold tomato in the oven
